    <title lang="en">Wild Rockies</title>
    <desc lang="en">The air is thin and cold, trees can't even live here -­- it's not exactly a welcoming place to live. But animals like mountain goats and bighorn sheep and even black bears manage to skitter around these peaks with ease. We'll take a look at how these creatures manage to defy gravity, among some of the highest peaks on the continent.</desc>
    <category lang="en">Wildlife</category>
    <episode-num system="xmltv_ns">0.1.</episode-num>
